{"tid":1421012,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"係大家批評和理非無用嘅時候 請想起係你地係集會現場叫人去幫手","createTime":"2019-08-06T06:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T07:20:57.000Z","uid":24173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b28cea06ed5a8827f0d0375a08b45d91dd2ea955","tid":1421012,"uid":24173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:34:59.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n睇左幾十個post<br />\n最後都係批評和理非<br />\n無諗過佢地好多都無出過去<br />\n係集會現場 聽你講完就跟你地上<br />\n前線又叫人企散 廢事人踩人<br />\n返到屋企又話後排太驚青 縮到後一後<br />\n<br />\n和理非好多無gear<br />\n大家叫佢地自備係岩<br />\n咁你知佢無gear仲叫人唔好退 企係度食<br />\n話無煙去後排<br />\n我想講大風到<br />\n街頭放 街尾都食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你叫人等煙散後 再返去無問題<br />\n但唔係叫人企定定食"},{"pid":"8819563d121cd5b93f82b3df8473422f7a624e43","tid":1421012,"uid":253833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:36:36.000Z","msg":"［借acc][純建議] 8月24日 全港罷買日 搞「靜」香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420749</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"30fc8d4216f5880c9785e6f2e134b22d265aba68","tid":1421012,"uid":264455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:37:43.000Z","msg":"提防分化撚，勇武唔撚割，和理非都唔撚割<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420725\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420725</a>"},{"pid":"e9198ff2291eb62a04e1d6d4878112c8dfb487ca","tid":1421012,"uid":24173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:39:14.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"350ed7fd513173f8dd30435793d83c6c65fbee73","tid":1421012,"uid":24173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:45:53.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"f945096a490bb748880b78ff0c1d1880044ec9c0","tid":1421012,"uid":24173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07